re stands on a rooftop with both arms lifted in a triumphant V shape, the city skyline behind him. Huge white outlined letters appear above him, first filling much of the sky with “JUST,” then resolving into the stacked phrase “JUST YOU.” Finally, the Just For Men Autostop box appears large on the left, showing the male face and hair on the package. To its right, white text reads “JUST YOU,” and beneath it a black rectangular banner says “& THE LOOK YOU WANT.” The silhouetted man remains below with arms raised against the skyline, while the product and slogan dominate the final image.",
